Name: Dance Dance Revolution Universe 3
Overview:
Over 70 songs with universal appeal with music from 70s to today

Everyone can play, accessible for all skill levels

DJ Mode makes its debut on the Xbox 360 and lets you create your own songs to dance to

Brand new "City Mode" lets you compete against bosses to become the ultimate champion

Enhanced "Quest Mode" lets you customize your own character with over 400 options of clothing, faces, skin tones, and hair styles
